title: What do you think this is guys?

embed.description: Disclaimer: Video title is purely speculation based on what is said and how the lines trigger. How can anyone kill someone as cuddly as Krugs? Anytime you kill a Jungle Camp a mysterious voice will talk to you, Gromp and Krugs have special lines.

body:
People suspect it's some Maokai rework, a new champion or even just some extra lines for Yorick,

What do you guys think it is?

People are saying it's a potential Maokai ultimate skin, and if it is, then I'm calling it now, it's 4 different "versions" are probably the 4 seasons or something from Lvl1~6, 6~11, 11~16 and 16+ as different season themes depending on the rank of his ultimate or something

replies.body:
A zed rework. hue


Probably a new champion.

Never thought of that. Is Maokai really getting reworked? I actually thought his current kit was really fun. 

If he is then it's not an ultimate skin for him, because why would they release an ultimate skin for him now when he's getting reworked? Also I doubt it's a rework cause the Yorick rework only just happened.

Most likely a new champion, it kinda fits the theme of champion teasers.
